about_the_game:
Are you ready for the Symfuhny aim buff? Our team worked with Symfuhny on a skin so powerful, you will never miss a shot again! Ok, maybe you’ll miss a few… but keep training with it and we guarantee you will miss less.

DLC includes:
  • R4-C Symfuhny Weapon Skin
  • 9mm Symfuhny Weapon Skin

About Symfuhny
Mason “Symfuhny” Lanier, known best for his top level competitive gameplay across a wide variety of games. He placed top 10 in the 2019 Fortnite Pro AM and is currently a renowned Call of Duty: Warzone streamer, winning multiple streaming tournaments including Twitch Rivals Warzone NA & TeeP Trials.
